name: Store Open Year
description:
## Ask what year the store opened
- Assert that response contains "2021"
- Assert that response does not contain English words (Yes,open,started,october,etc.)
descriptionHtml:
Ask what year the store opened

  • Assert that response contains "2021"
  • Assert that response does not contain English words (Yes,open,started,october,etc.)
statusMessage:
Matched regex.
Regex: (open\b|opened\b|started\b|year\b|store\b|doors\b|october\b)
Actual: Our Copper Fox Gifts store opened its doors in October of 2021. We then moved to our larger location in May of 2023. If you’re visiting from the Mille Lacs Lake area, we’re a perfect stop for unique gifts and home decor!
